{
  "texts": [
    "We identify and list the most notable challenges in automatic plankton recognition and provide detailed descriptions of the solutions found in the plankton recognition literature for each challenge.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first comprehensive survey focusing exclusively on plankton recognition and the specific challenges related to it.",
    "The rest of the paper is organized as follows.",
    "In Sect. 2, the plankton imaging, i.e., imaging instruments and existing image datasets are reviewed.",
    "In Sect. 3, automatic plankton recognition including feature engineering and CNNs are discussed."
  ]
}